10 An Act relating to crimes and punishments; amending
21 O.S. 2021, Section 856.3, which relates to gang-
11 related offenses; modifying reference to certain
offense; updating statutory language and references;
12 and providing an effective date.
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 856.3, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 856.3. Any person who attempts or commits a gang-
19 related offense as a condition of membership in a criminal street
20 gang or while in association with any criminal street gang or gang
21 member shall be guilty of a felony offense. Upon punishable upon
22 conviction, the violator shall be punished by incarceration
23 imprisonment in the custody of the Department of Corrections for a
24 term of five (5) years, which shall be in addition to any other
