1 pena lty imposed. For purposes of this section, “criminal street
2 gang” is defined by subsection F of Section 856 of Title 21 of the
3 Oklahoma Statutes this title and “gang-related offense” means those
4 offenses enumerated in paragraphs 1 through 16 of subsection F of
5 Section 856 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma Statutes this title.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
